lesson.title: What's Next?
lesson.summary: Here's how to keep building your NLP expertise!

concepts.title: Ready to Level Up with NLP?

atoms.text:
It's been our pleasure taking you through just a small taste of the NLP experience.

If you're ready to fully unlock the power of NLP, [come join us in the Nanodegree classroom](https://www.udacity.com/course/natural-language-processing-nanodegree--nd892). You'll get complete access to:

* Cutting edge material on Natural Language Processing and Speech Recognition.
* Hands-on projects where you'll build models and test them on real data.
* **Your own AI mentor** to answer your questions and provide reviews on your project

[Click here to get started!](https://www.udacity.com/course/natural-language-processing-nanodegree--nd892)
